      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 1185,
      "message": "Also, not using nulls in general is a good practice.\n\n@Chris: If you look at how this function is later used, it is only iterated over (it's never modified). This means you can use `Collections.emptyList()` instead of the empty `Vector`:\n```\nfinal List<GroupDefinition> nonNullGroupDefinitions =\n  (groupDefinitions == null) ? Collections.emptyList() : groupDefinitions;\n```",
